snippet.title: 🎄⛳ Holiday Hideaway Teaser Trailer - Walkabout Mini Golf
snippet.description:
Celebrate the holidays December 5 in a quiet cabin near the North Pole. Frolic through the decorations, presents, and Christmas charm of this nostalgic adventure that is sure to be on your list.

Available on Meta Quest, PSVR2, Pico, SteamVR and iOS devices.
